ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of REBECCA CHARTRAND of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Allan B. Adam, whose term has expired.
